# ── Firebase (Phase 4 push notifications) ──────────────────────────
# Service-account keys are SENSITIVE — never commit. Belt-and-suspenders
# patterns so an accidental drop into the repo is ignored.
*firebase-adminsdk*.json
**/firebase-service-account.json
# NOTE: google-services.json + GoogleService-Info.plist ARE committed on
# purpose — Firebase *client* API keys are restricted by bundle ID +
# Security Rules and are safe in client code; EAS builds need them present.

